# Issue Faced

Inside Ubuntu

```bash
docker ps
```

Initially received

```
The command 'docker' could not be found in this WSL 2 distro.
```

### Cause

Docker Desktop was installed but Ubuntu was not integrated with Docker Desktop.

### Solution

1. Open Docker Desktop
2. Go to

```
Settings
    Resources
        WSL Integration
```

3. Enable Ubuntu
4. Click Apply & Restart
5. Restart WSL

```powershell
wsl --shutdown
```

6. Open Ubuntu again

Docker commands started working successfully.

